data.description: New - Raised Ranch built with total of approximately 2000 square feet of living space between upstairs and finished area in basement. The home features living room,  dining room and kitchen all with cathedral ceilings and hardwood floors. Kitchen has a peninsula and granite countertops. There are 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, one being off the main bedroom. The basement has a huge family room and a 1/2 bath. There is also a Trex deck off the back slider, Central Air,  and  a one car garage under and  lots of parking. Should be completed in 30 days. . Home is located close to shopping, schools, and major routes. OPEN HOUSE - SATURDAY AND SUNDAY, NOVEMBER 4 &5 FROM 12-2. ALL OFFERS TO BE IN BY MONDAY, NOVEMBER 6.
